        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "briefDescription": "The Mukhyamantri Balika (Intermediate Pass) Protsahan Yojana is a scheme by the Bihar government aimed at promoting girl child education, curbing child marriages, reducing fertility rates, and empowering girls to become self-reliant. ",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &amp;quot;Mukhyamantri Balika (Intermediate Pass) Protsahan Yojana&amp;quot;, a component of the &amp;quot;Mukhyamantri Kanya Utthan Yojana&amp;quot;, launched by the Education Department, Bihar, focuses on the socio-economic upliftment of girls in Bihar. The scheme provides monetary incentives to unmarried girls who have cleared their intermediate examinations from recognized schools or madrasas within Bihar. \n",
        "benefits_md": "\n  - **Financial Assistance:** ₹10,000/- for girls passing intermediate in 2021; ₹25,000/- in 2022 and later.\n&lt;br&gt;\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "",
