          "process_md": "> **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the Registration [page](https://medhasoft.bih.nic.in/medhamat2022/(S(isowffkahr0cb41idfmeymls))/Default.aspx).\n**Step 2:** Scroll down below and click on &quot;Students Click Here To Apply&quot;.\n**Step 3:** Read the instructions and click on the check-boxes. Click on &quot;Continue&quot;.\n**Step 4:** Enter all the mandatory details and create a new password. Validate the Captcha code.\n**Step 5:** Click on “Submit” to generate the login ID and Password.\n> **Application Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the Login [page](https://medhasoft.bih.nic.in/medhamat2022/(S(isowffkahr0cb41idfmeymls))/Login.aspx).\n**Step 2:** Enter all the mandatory details and upload all the required documents.\n**Step 3:** Recheck all entries before final submission, no modifications can be made in the application after final submission.\n**Step 4:** Click on “Submit” and take a printout of a copy of the submitted application.\n> **Check application Details:** Click [Here](https://medhasoft.bih.nic.in/medhamat2022/(S(isowffkahr0cb41idfmeymls))/StudentStatus.aspx).\n\n> **Payment Done Information:** Click [Here](https://medhasoft.bih.nic.in/medhamat2022/(S(isowffkahr0cb41idfmeymls))/PaymentDoneList.aspx).\n\n<br>\n\n> ***Helpdesk:*** \n\nFor technical problems: Click [Here](https://medhasoft.bih.nic.in/medhamat2022/(S(isowffkahr0cb41idfmeymls))/Helpdesk.aspx).\n"
        }
