      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n- The applicant must be a resident of Bihar.\n- The applicant must be an unmarried girl.\n- She must have passed the intermediate examination from a recognized school, madrasa, or institution in Bihar.\n- The examination must have been conducted in 2021 or later.\n- The applicant must have a valid bank account.\n\n",
